data.description: This stunning 4-bedroom, 2.5-bath home is nestled in the sought-after Creekside Subdivision, offering a captivating blend of comfort, space, and an idyllic location. As you arrive, be greeted by a meticulously manicured lawn and an inviting covered front porch. Upon entering, an open floor plan unfolds seamlessly, creating a perfect ambiance for entertaining. Adorned with beautiful wood floors that flow effortlessly throughout the main level, this home exudes warmth and elegance. The eat-in kitchen is a culinary masterpiece, featuring gleaming granite countertops, a stylish tile backsplash, and an island that provides ample prep space. Ascend the stairs to the upper level, where you will find an oversized primary bedroom that awaits your dreams. This private retreat boasts a cozy sitting area and an ensuite bath complete with a double vanity and a luxurious soaking tub. Three additional bedrooms and a full bathroom with a double vanity offer ample space for family, guests, or home office needs. Step out the backdoor onto an oversized, covered patio, the perfect sanctuary for al fresco dining and entertaining. This sprawling backyard, one of the largest in the subdivision, is fully fenced, providing a private oasis for relaxation and play. Strategically located near Lake Acworth, Kennesaw State University, I-75, parks, and the vibrant shopping and dining options of Kennesaw, this home offers an exceptional blend of convenience and tranquility. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exquisite residence your own.
